testsuite.name: MessageService Tests

testcase.name: Should save satellite split data successfully
Should handle different message array lengths
Should handle satellite names case insensitively
Should throw LocationException when position calculation fails
Should process TopSecretSplit successfully with 3 satellites
Should clear satellites cache after successful split processing
Should throw MessageException when message reconstruction fails
Should throw LocationException when insufficient satellites for split processing
